review_blob: From a bottle which was half a year past its date, however this probably didnt affect the taste or appearance. O.K. brew, some chocolate, however a bit thin and the smoked flavours are only limited present. There are many better (smoked)porters available...
Draft at Oersoep brewery, October 2015. Excellent imperial stout with coffee flavours and a nice sweetness, however not too sweet.
